node.text:
Circuit breaker day 26: made 2 different toasts with whatever I can find in my pantry. 😉 .
.
🥪 'Pizza' toast with a tomato base, topped with chicken sausages and cheddar cheese
🥪 Garlic toast with homemade garlic spread and a dash of black pepper

Which toast do you prefer? 🙅‍♀️ .

#sgunited #circuitbreaker #stayhomesg
@cooking_is_beautiful Thank you and enjoy your weekend! 😘😘
@things_to_eat_in_korea Thank you and have a safe weekend! 😘
@xxoo_cin it’s ok, cos I LOOOVVEEE garlic 😂
@vnm_lee I also had both as one is never enough for me 😅 I am so full now. Belly-happy! 😉
I take both cos I m a big eater when it comes to breakfast!! 😅 So yummy my dear, enjoy!! 🤗😋❤️
@xiueyyy Thanks Jas! Enjoy yours too and have an amazing Saturday with Nigel! 😘 Stay safe! 💕
What an awesome breakfast, Cin! Delicious good start to the morning ☺️
@35sweetpotato 🙌 I ate both! 😅😉 Thanks and have a lovely Saturday! 😘💕
I want both !!😍. Perfect breakfast to kickstart the day 😋❤️❤️
@floatsam_and_jetsam Enjoy your day and eat more yummy food 😉
@erikas_food_acc Thank you, Erika! Have a lovely weekend 😘

I want the garlic toast pls... with the sausage on the side....😁
